General.Name: Moment Group AB
General.Description: Moment Group AB, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the entertainment business in Sweden, Norway, and Denmark. The company operates through Live Entertainment, Immersive Venues, and Event segments. It produces and markets musicals, theatrical productions, shows, and concerts, as well as creates special-order entertainment events; and arranges artists for corporate customers. In addition, the company operates food and beverage business; SHOWTIC.se, a ticket booking site that markets and sells tickets; and offers brand engagement services, which includes digital events, live events, content marketing, and sponsoring. Moment Group AB was incorporated in 1987 and is based in Gothenburg, Sweden.
